@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v1 + 0.20)
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v2 = (0.54 / ((v2 + 0.91 - v1 + 0.26) + (v1 + 0.92 * v1 + 0.37)))
    v0 = (0.28 / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.14) + v2))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.52)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.24 / v2 + 0.47)) + tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
